==網上觀看==
在2006年1月，[[蘋果公司|蘋果公司]]（Apple Inc.）開始在[[iTunes_Store|iTunes Store]]出售迷你影集、第一及二季全集。<ref>{{cite press|url=http://www.thefutoncritic.com/news/2005/12/22/sci-fi-inside-battlestar-galactica-to-premiere-on-the-itunes-music-store-20159/20051222scifi01/|title=Sci Fi Inside: Battlestar Galactica' to Premiere on the iTunes Music Store|publisher=Sci Fi|date=December 22, 2005|accessdate=July 13, 2011}}</ref>2007年12月，包括《太空堡壘卡拉狄加》系列在內的一切[[NBC環球|NBC環球]]（NBC Universal）的作品都在iTunes下架。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://tech.fortune.cnn.com/2007/12/03/nbc-pulls-its-tv-shows-from-apple-itunes/|title=NBC pulls its TV shows from Apple iTunes|publisher=Fortune Tech|date=December 3, 2007|accessdate=July 13, 2011|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120515220011/http://tech.fortune.cnn.com/2007/12/03/nbc-pulls-its-tv-shows-from-apple-itunes/|archive-date=2012-05-15|dead-url=yes}}</ref>要到翌年8月，NBC環球才宣佈回歸iTunes，《太空堡壘卡拉狄加》再次開放購買。<ref>{{cite press|url=http://www.thefutoncritic.com/news/2008/09/09/nbc-universal-returns-to-the-itunes-store--28735/20080909nbc03/|title=NBC Universal Returns to the iTunes Store|publisher=NBC|date=September 9, 2008|accessdate=July 13, 2011}}</ref>2009年2月，高清版本的《太空堡壘卡拉狄加》在[[英國|英國]]的iTunes Store開放購買。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.igizmo.co.uk/articles/news/978-home-entertainment-hd-revolution-gathers-pace-uk-itunes-store|title=HD revolution gathers pace in UK iTunes Store|date=February 6, 2009|accessdate=February 6, 2009|publisher=iGizmo|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://archive.is/20120801203737/http://www.igizmo.co.uk/articles/news/978-home-entertainment-hd-revolution-gathers-pace-uk-itunes-store|archivedate=2012年8月1日}}</ref>

